<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"78da24f","css":".pc78da24f{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:0px 0px 12px 0px !important;}.pc78da24f__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pc78da24f .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#707070;font-size:12px;font-family:DM Sans;font-weight:400;}","content":"\u003cbr\u003eAll preparation materials, sketches, visuals, including the electronic files used to create the project remain the property of Felix Ayoola. The final artwork/digital files will become the property of the client in this proposal ONLY upon final payment of the project.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eIf final payment is NOT received as agreed, and set out in the initial proposal, all designs and concepts will remain the property of Felix Ayoola until payment is received. If there are issues with the final payment, I reserve the right to reuse or amend any of these ideas for other clients, or to be used freely as concepts in my\u003cbr\u003eportfolio.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eShould the client attempt to use/modify/alter/replicate or steal any of my ideas without making agreed final payment, I will take immediate legal counsel.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFelix Ayoola reserves the rights to show any artwork, ideas, sketched created for this project as examples of client work. This can be during the project, and also on completion. If you have any specific secrecy/stealth mode requirements, kindly mention this before agreeing to the proposal.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eFinal payment ensures that ONLY the agreed design becomes the client's property. Any previous ideas / concepts remain the property of Felix Ayoola unless prior agreement has \u003cbr\u003ebeen made.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":"DM Sans","color":"#707070","margin":{"top":"0px","right":"0px","bottom":"12px","left":"0px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc78da24f" data-block-id="78da24f"><div class="pc78da24f__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph"><br>All preparation materials, sketches, visuals, including the electronic files used to create the project remain the property of Felix Ayoola. The final artwork/digital files will become the property of the client in this proposal ONLY upon final payment of the project.<br><br>If final payment is NOT received as agreed, and set out in the initial proposal, all designs and concepts will remain the property of Felix Ayoola until payment is received. If there are issues with the final payment, I reserve the right to reuse or amend any of these ideas for other clients, or to be used freely as concepts in my<br>portfolio.<br><br>Should the client attempt to use/modify/alter/replicate or steal any of my ideas without making agreed final payment, I will take immediate legal counsel.<br><br>Felix Ayoola reserves the rights to show any artwork, ideas, sketched created for this project as examples of client work. This can be during the project, and also on completion. If you have any specific secrecy/stealth mode requirements, kindly mention this before agreeing to the proposal.<br><br>Final payment ensures that ONLY the agreed design becomes the client's property. Any previous ideas / concepts remain the property of Felix Ayoola unless prior agreement has <br>been made.</p></div></div>
