<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pc5ddbd0b" data-block-id="5ddbd0b"><div class="pc5ddbd0b__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph"><br>If you are unhappy about the progress of the project, feel we are not finding an appropriate angle, and/or feel that you voice and input is not being acknowledged, kindly discuss this with me. I would encourage that we schedule a call rather than e-mail ; I am very easy going and even easier to talk to.<br><br>It is completely crucial that we are both completely clear about the objectives and aims before commencing. Now is the time to be open with your thoughts, doubts and/or <br>concerns.<br><br>Once you have signed and filled in the details below, <strong>kindly send this form back to flxayoola@gmail.com</strong><br><br>Once you have signed and sent back this proposal, kindly arrange the first payment so that we can get started with this project. Until this is received, I am unable to book your project in and other jobs may take precedence in this time.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

