<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-list pc1419236" data-block-id="1419236"><div class="pc1419236__overlay"><ol><li>Acknowledgment and Proposal Receipt:&nbsp;Upon receiving your signed proposal, we express our gratitude for your prompt action. Your commitment to this project is greatly appreciated. We understand the importance of timely communication and are pleased to have your proposal in hand.</li><li>Payment Arrangement:&nbsp;Kindly proceed to arrange the initial payment as outlined in the proposal. This step is crucial for us to initiate work on your project. Until we receive the payment, we regret that we cannot secure a booking for your project. Please be assured that once the payment is processed, we will prioritize your project and allocate the necessary resources.</li><li>Project Priority and Booking:&nbsp;We value your trust in our services. However, please note that until the first payment is confirmed, other jobs may take precedence. Our commitment to excellence remains unwavering, and we look forward to collaborating with you on this exciting project.</li></ol></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/list -->

