<!-- wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph {"uniqueId":"b720ba5","css":".pcb720ba5{border-style:none;border-color:#000000;border-width:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:0px 0px 86px 0px !important;}.pcb720ba5__overlay{padding:0px 0px 0px 0px !important;}.pcb720ba5 .pc-paragraph{text-align:left;color:#707070;font-size:12px;font-family:DM Sans;font-weight:400;}","content":"You take full responsibility for ensuring that the company/product/name is legally free/available before the work is started. Should any legal issue arise with the naming after the project has been completed, no refunds are possible; neither am I legally responsible for any problems thus arising. Kindly ensure that the name that you are using is free and legally safe to use before committing to an identity development project.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eProject names during a projects are costly and challenging to implement and can cause significant delays. If a change of name is required mid-way during a project and signifcant exploration has already been presented, a recalculation of the total cost of the project to allow for the reworking will be brought forward. In some cases this can be as much as double the initial agreed cost.\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003eKindly ensure that the name that you are using has been subject to appropriate checks, is not in use by someone else, and/or infringes on any other registered trademark, business name etc.","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":"DM Sans","color":"#707070","margin":{"top":"0px","right":"0px","bottom":"86px","left":"0px"}} -->
<div class="wp-block-proposal-crafter-paragraph pcb720ba5" data-block-id="b720ba5"><div class="pcb720ba5__overlay"><p class="pc-paragraph">You take full responsibility for ensuring that the company/product/name is legally free/available before the work is started. Should any legal issue arise with the naming after the project has been completed, no refunds are possible; neither am I legally responsible for any problems thus arising. Kindly ensure that the name that you are using is free and legally safe to use before committing to an identity development project.<br><br>Project names during a projects are costly and challenging to implement and can cause significant delays. If a change of name is required mid-way during a project and signifcant exploration has already been presented, a recalculation of the total cost of the project to allow for the reworking will be brought forward. In some cases this can be as much as double the initial agreed cost.<br><br>Kindly ensure that the name that you are using has been subject to appropriate checks, is not in use by someone else, and/or infringes on any other registered trademark, business name etc.</p></div></div>
<!-- /wp:proposal-crafter/paragraph -->

